18 Nov 2009 (GMT+8) Ray Rashif <schivmeister@gmail.com>

	* Moved from [testing] 2.8.3-1 to [stable] 2.8.4-1
	* New buildscripts

###############################
# General Package Information #
###############################

Differences from archlinux/extra/ardour:

	* LV2 support
	* Use included libs instead of syslibs
		- system libs break upstream support
	* Wiimote support; WIIMOTE=1
		- cwiid: buildtime mandatory, runtime optional
	* Freesound support; FREESOUND=1
	* PKGBUILD; build options; deps cleanup
		- clarified a few things with Paul Davis, upstream
	* Other minor ammendments
